strings: Here rests my dear daughter Shai.
<voice_0x0100181F><se_low>Jungmi: I want to tell you a secret that this was not the resting place for Diya's daughter and her mother.
<voice_0x01001820><se_low>Jungmi: After all the hard work, he should be buried with El Torrio.
<voice_0x01001821><se_low>Jungmi: At least for now, we can be together until the day we die...
